name: Angry Ape Army Evolution #2979
description:
A mysterious electric surge on the infamous "Monkey Island" summoned a gateway that leads to different worlds of evolved apes, linking alternate dimensions and parallel universes.

This token represents one of those "Evolved Apes". Keep it safe to increase your battle advantage or use it to spawn a Goliath x Golem by combining 4 evo apes.

**Long live the Revolution!**

asset_contract.name: Angry Ape Army Evolution Collection
asset_contract.description:
The Angry Ape Army have modified their own kind to create "Evolved Apes." 
These lab grown apes are now roaming the metaverse destroying and taking control of all that come in it's path. Take control of an "Evolved Ape" and have superior battle advantage or spawn a Goliath x Golem by combining 4 evo apes. 


**Join the Revolution!!!**
